Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚倒在了正门口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  九澄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的杀人鬼少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的真面目居然是…栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  快回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就到上课时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后图书室见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？栉名田请假了吗  真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:23.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛しさはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:23.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱之彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:29.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみへと続いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:29.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接连着伤
