Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  身体又不舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这里总是拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里呀  像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想听香织姐姐的示范演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那份名单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你才把名单交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这镇子原本就不需要那些人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偏偏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  并不是指你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用在意  我只是打杂的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成工作了就立刻从这里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的事是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还需要去接麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些事想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想听听伯父的意见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于嫦娥狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神原本是本地人敬拜的土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说从前这一带生活着狼群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神化身成狼并守护着城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得之前和博士君的父亲说的…大神和嫦娥狼的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说山里还有嫦娥狼生存着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是大型野生动物能够悄然生存的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大神传说还流传着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥狼就会继续生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了这样的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我更觉得是恰好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过大神的信仰和传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩盖了至今仍生存着的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那嫦娥狼现在还存在着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但那也许和我们所想的狼是不同的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是传说以前生活在这一带的大型狼——嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是越是调查它的真相就越是模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能证明它存在过的证据太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  嫦娥镇以外的地方都不承认其存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个我个人的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许嫦娥狼和普通的狼是完全不同的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如是拥有人类般智慧的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为凶月  带来不幸的红色月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不吉利的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道彗星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样被当作不吉利的象征的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如传言中数年后将要到来的哈雷彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是不吉利的象征之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻它是会带来疾病的凶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那彗星一样被当作不吉利的象征的  就是凶月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天的气温和湿度都比以往要高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷热的天气持续到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特产的八朔也收获不济
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做各种调查的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了含有嫦娥狼和凶月这些关键词的「嫦娥数数歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超自然魂告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些歌词里一定隐藏着什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是常有的设定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  我现在打算去地方资料馆调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对了  如果找到嫦娥数数歌的歌词的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能听取下伯父的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会告诉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又偷懒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始学习不是挺认真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授都夸奖你很勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在却人不像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得地质学没意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃饭就得花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此必须要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你又是为了什么来到大学的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老在外面吃饭也不考虑下花费  还喊穷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做饭不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑脸我真的觉得很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来打个招呼多好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真没想到您还会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就这么觉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生的笑脸一定很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  刚才的音色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还远远不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想去东京的音大认真学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能离开这座城镇所以放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天来学习小提琴的学生烤了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起来品尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要为三重子复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人好像回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  麻奈做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？我为了香织姐姐努力做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我们就开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  我们已经在「中心」保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我想查一下「嫦娥数数歌」的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌啊  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌…  数数歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在里面的D13号书架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月盈盈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨镰下矣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「落神」的仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  麻奈她的话  已经被令尊接走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是刚好错过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才该道歉呢  来得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说谎  请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是在这里  一个女人拿着巨大的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你现在方便么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也见过杀人现场？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过那已经是四年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我也和你一样  想去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可警局却空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人现场也消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被杀的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新珠三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩在同一所大学读书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为了写毕业论文  而造访了这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却万万没有想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而至于当时那不知底细的杀人集团…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个杀人集团之中  拿着巨型镰刀的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们班上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田眠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这些话  反正也不会有人信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法向任何人谈起这事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我想  如果是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话  一定是能够相信我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我说…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贤木俊一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…  欢迎回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去香织小姐那儿去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果说她已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洋葱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  我能进来么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他好担…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐她说  从今天开始  不准备再教我拉小提琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐她…  没有说原因么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因为看到大姐姐她有时无精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想多陪陪她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  我也很担心香织小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆下回就不以上课的名义  而是去探望她如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人么？  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喊破喉咙也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那样么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那样」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你是不是也成了「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是你的恋人？  还是你喜欢的对象？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你的对象  也像摘花前辈那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花前辈  是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚大哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  非常喜欢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他能够给我一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我被送到了这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神人」是指什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你还没有听说么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  为人身  而又非人之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没窗子对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这里应该是地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下雨  排水沟中的流水声  就从天花板上传来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的那位摘花前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于戒律所定的「落神之式」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落神？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个说法  就是被处决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为「神人」的前辈  和我接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我便不再为人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人身  而非人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上现在  也对气味非常敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上  有着「神堕人」的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:17.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:17.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.91,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:49.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:49.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消无痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.57,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结若缚君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:07.18,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堕ちて行く決意が許されるまで　愛なのと信じたり
