Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:14.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:20.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交わる闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:20.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交织暗之乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:27.09,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでいく　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:27.09,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:37.79,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが夢見た時の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:37.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我梦  彼情歌
